        <span class="transform-label">SWITCHMAP</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="transform-list">
        <li>Perl + SNMP polling (redundant with LibreNMS)</li>
        <li>Static HTML generation via cron</li>
        <li>No search or filtering capability</li>
        <li>No device grouping or organization</li>
        <li>Unstyled table output</li>
        <li>Last updated: 2016</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="transform-arrow">&#8594;</div>
    <div class="transform-card after">
      <div class="transform-header">
        <span class="transform-icon">&#9989;</span>
        <span class="transform-label">MY SOLUTION: PORTGRID</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="transform-list">
        <li>Built on LibreNMS API (zero polling overhead)</li>
        <li>60-second auto-refresh I implemented</li>
        <li>Instant search I designed from scratch</li>
        <li>Drag-and-drop grouping with dnd-kit</li>
        <li>Modern UI with dark/light mode</li>
        <li>Actively maintained: 2026</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Architecture Diagram -->
